{"tid":382633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"海味舖被圍防水板　反困洪水5小時　轟署方荒謬","createTime":"2017-09-01T00:00:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-01T05:54:06.000Z","uid":81228,"like":37,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"3d9f5f9f7725510c7b3ba5780bc543bd47602243","tid":382633,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T00:00:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/116113/thumbnail/aabaa99f96f0b119db9c4e15fc49d484.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F116113%2Fthumbnail%2Faabaa99f96f0b119db9c4e15fc49d484.jpg&h=25c966ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n撰文：\t魯嘉裕 蔡正邦<br />\n<br />\n颱風天鴿上周三（8月23日）吹襲，大澳慘成水浸重災區，居民商戶大批財物浸毀，損失慘重。然而政府於事前準備多項防洪工程，包括興建價值1.5億元的防水堤、安裝水浸預警系統及於水浸前於多個高危位置安裝擋水板等，均無阻洪水淹城，其中於永安街一間近岸邊海味店，更於天鴿吹襲前離奇被渠務署人員於店前圍起擋水板，導致水浸時「防水變困水」，店舖被及胸洪水圍困5小時，大街卻安然無恙。<br />\n<br />\n店主稱，事件令他痛失數十萬海味及電器，炮轟渠務署及木土工程拓展署做法荒謬，「點解唔可以圍係鋪頭後面，係咪將我間鋪當儲水庫」，店主其後向兩署代表對質，對方卻互相推卸責任，稱會研究其意見。然而下周日（3日）再有風暴可能吹襲香港，渠務署代表稱如有水浸仍然會再圍封海味鋪，店主母親憤怒稱，「你哋再圍我實告你！」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/805343/xlarge/bde4e0c3ef48ce350008fb120abd9928.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F805343%2Fxlarge%2Fbde4e0c3ef48ce350008fb120abd9928.jpg&h=57fa35f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n永安街一間海味店於上周水浸時被渠務署人員於店前圍上防水板。（蔡正邦攝）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/805344/xlarge/2bb5fd5b965ff2d60c674baed59bd322.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F805344%2Fxlarge%2F2bb5fd5b965ff2d60c674baed59bd322.jpg&h=329a1e79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n店舖被及胸洪水圍困5小時，當時街道上已退水，惟圍板內的區域已被水圍困。（受訪者提供）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/805351/xlarge/398b60f1bc9a360db616d48caf8bf0cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F805351%2Fxlarge%2F398b60f1bc9a360db616d48caf8bf0cd.jpg&h=1080b8c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/805352/xlarge/f24dd4b09fb1e0ccd37960ef6fff29cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F805352%2Fxlarge%2Ff24dd4b09fb1e0ccd37960ef6fff29cf.jpg&h=330abdaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/805353/xlarge/63d30be9170d99e7adbf7260a7820b55.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F805353%2Fxlarge%2F63d30be9170d99e7adbf7260a7820b55.jpg&h=3c3e787b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/805354/xlarge/b154dc0a670896747372841205d054bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F805354%2Fxlarge%2Fb154dc0a670896747372841205d054bf.jpg&h=2a50ab54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/805348/xlarge/06e71e2fece004042ccee40f3e25f735.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F805348%2Fxlarge%2F06e71e2fece004042ccee40f3e25f735.jpg&h=51f52cc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n受災海味店位於永安街，店主池先生與家人為大澳居民，約半年前創業於上址經營海味店，其鋪位後方為岸邊，除其店舖外，岸邊其他位置均已圍上擋水板。池解釋渠務署圍板事件早有前因，於2011年木土工程拓展署曾多次與池開會，當時舖位仍是空地，署方稱水浸時會於其鋪位位置圍上擋水板，防止水浸入大街，池當時要求署方於其舖位後方，即岸邊位置圍板，「咁咪直接喺岸邊擋住啲水，唔使浸到我哋間舖」，池指當時署方同意其要求。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/805345/xlarge/0659a4cc7d2e52e0e55d7376b21f4151.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F805345%2Fxlarge%2F0659a4cc7d2e52e0e55d7376b21f4151.jpg&h=4d5dd045&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鋪位後方為岸邊，除其店舖外，岸邊其他位置均已圍上擋水板。（蔡正邦攝）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/805346/xlarge/4a4cd78e12b20b61c5485d5b75f90792.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F805346%2Fxlarge%2F4a4cd78e12b20b61c5485d5b75f90792.jpg&h=84ad7ce7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n於上周水浸發生後，渠務署人員仍前來鎖緊圍板。（受訪者提供）<br />\n<br />\n直到今年天鴿吹襲前一晚（22日），負責工程的渠務署人員到其店舖圍板時，卻將圍板圍於店鋪前方，事後更沒有知會過池先生。到風暴當日，池先生稱其父親於下午返回店舖時方發現事件，當時圍板內的水已浸及胸，加上圍板內被渠務署人員放滿工程雜物，池父無法進入店內「救貨」，只能白看店鋪受浸，結果超過30萬的花膠海味及電器被水浸毀。有街坊拍下照片，顯示當時街道上已退水，惟圍板內的區域仍被水圍困。<br />\n<br />\n池先生指署方違反承諾於其店前圍板，事前事後更完全沒有通知他們，「咁係咪即係犧牲我哋去保住條街？打風水浸係天災，但今次損失咁嚴重就係人禍」，池與母親前晚（30日）於居民大會中當面向渠務署及木土工程拓展署對質，雙方卻互相推卸責任，「渠務署就話圍板係對方設計，木土工程拓展署就話啲板係對方圍」，僅稱會回去研究其意見。然而兩、三日後另一風暴有機會再吹襲本港，渠務署代表稱如水浸會再次圍板，池母親憤怒稱如是會控告署方，池稱「咁係咪將我間舖當儲水庫」，擔心屆時再次蒙受損失。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/116113/-%E5%A4%A9%E9%B4%BF%E6%B7%B9%E5%A4%A7%E6%BE%B3-%E6%B5%B7%E5%91%B3%E8%88%96%E8%A2%AB%E5%9C%8D%E9%98%B2%E6%B0%B4%E6%9D%BF-%E5%8F%8D%E5%9B%B0%E6%B4%AA%E6%B0%B45%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82-%E8%BD%9F%E7%BD%B2%E6%96%B9%E8%8D%92%E8%AC%AC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F116113%2F-%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E9%25B4%25BF%25E6%25B7%25B9%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25BE%25B3-%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%2591%25B3%25E8%2588%2596%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%259C%258D%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E6%259D%25BF-%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%259B%25B0%25E6%25B4%25AA%25E6%25B0%25B45%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%2599%2582-%25E8%25BD%259F%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%258D%2592%25E8%25AC%25AC&d=NupbHYB5KW%2FHdrkWaglYOAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=76007914\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/116113/-%E5%A4%A9%E9%B4%BF%E6%B7%B9%E5%A4%A7%E6%BE%B3-%E6%B5%B7%E5%91%B3%E8%88%96%E8%A2%AB%E5%9C%8D%E9%98%B2%E6%B0%B4%E6%9D%BF-%E5%8F%8D%E5%9B%B0%E6%B4%AA%E6%B0%B45%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82-%E8%BD%9F%E7%BD%B2%E6%96%B9%E8%8D%92%E8%AC%AC</a>"},{"pid":"56ff5e6793c893cb91ff2060c153655f0a33e887","tid":382633,"uid":59898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T00:02:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c805a9528df2ee7cee53cf4f5a99ca4192ee0c4","tid":382633,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":36,"score":-36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T00:14:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b4b524d4c3e2361e04d0994d18b88e97026a406e","tid":382633,"uid":86756,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T00:20:25.000Z","msg":"半年前先開鋪<br />\n真係慘，錢都未賺到就蝕大本"},{"pid":"ede50759a715a7dd68dda64921aaa49d09c68d1d","tid":382633,"uid":25050,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T00:21:51.000Z","msg":"真係防水喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60211fe35540da36f80acfd8597c0181bc93e588","tid":382633,"uid":39871,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T00:26:48.000Z","msg":"塊板又幾犀利wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a23e043b118a4db434d32fcb814d203906be2ab4","tid":382633,"uid":20867,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T00:30:25.000Z","msg":"票投民建聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aab595cf43532e38eb6a5f43feb1602fd3810f8","tid":382633,"uid":69924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T00:32:02.000Z","msg":"個舖位之前係空地"},{"pid":"7a341ae8855e05838965585221714956481595af","tid":382633,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T00:35:16.000Z","msg":"2011年當時鋪位仍然是空地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n過去六年起間鋪出黎個時有冇合法申請？地政屋宇署知唔知先？正常渠務署會收到circulation俾comment。如果政府有錯一定要claim啦。<br />\n<br />\n2011年佢話反對過，雙方有冇白紙黑字紀錄？過去幾年如果渠務署用過圍板，佢知唔知先？"},{"pid":"4d46461da93b428471d1d5a69f24dd433b59b735","tid":382633,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T00:42:46.000Z","msg":"蓄洪池"},{"pid":"ccd878418c93e2f1a2857e8109590d2336cf596a","tid":382633,"uid":188,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T00:44:47.000Z","msg":"為左大部分人利益 你忍耐下啦牛頭人"},{"pid":"5098651efea2666947f33a707a113e5dfcf85c5d","tid":382633,"uid":39012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,